  "text": "Publications\nThe NYU Shanghai Magazine tells the evolving story of the first Sino-US research university in the world. It captures the lives of our faculty, students, alumni, and administrators. By chronicling what it takes to build a distinctive institution with a global student body and vision, we celebrate groundbreaking achievements, mark important moments in time, and take a glimpse into the future.\nHave Your Say\nGot a story idea or comment about this issue? Send your suggestions to shanghai.magazine@nyu.edu.\nGet Your Copy\nStep Inside NYU Shanghai\n10th Anniversary Edition\nSpring 2022, ISSUE 6\nSpring 2021, ISSUE 5\nSpring 2020, ISSUE 4\nSpring 2019, ISSUE 3\nSpring 2018, ISSUE 2\nSpring 2017, ISSUE 1",
